Nollywood actor, Timini Egbuson also known as Timini, has jokingly asked the Federal Government to completely lockdown on February 14 to stem the spread of COVID-19. This, he said, on his Twitter handle, will keep less Nigerians infected as lovers will have less contact. Timini’s tweeted: “We need a full national 24 hours lockdown on Valentine’s Day. This thing don dey spread too much.” Twitter users agreed with him, saying this is not the season to care so much about love.